1
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:34,990
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

2
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:37,979
[Episode 29]

3
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:41,110
[Joyful]

4
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:40,880
Shengli,

5
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:42,210
are you

6
00:01:42,229 --> 00:01:44,200
still selling leather shoes and jackets?

7
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:44,840
Leather shoes and jackets.

8
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,979
Business is pretty stable now,

9
00:01:45,979 --> 00:01:46,750
so I let the factory

10
00:01:46,750 --> 00:01:47,880
handle it directly.

11
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,080
We found a storefront

12
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,180
on Yabao Road.

13
00:01:50,450 --> 00:01:51,120
We're thinking of

14
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,560
selling some other things

15
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:55,550
to expand the business.

16
00:01:55,690 --> 00:01:57,100
Scale up the business.

17
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:59,190
I gotta say, Shengli

18
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:00,780
is a man of great vision.

19
00:02:01,350 --> 00:02:01,950
How so?

20
00:02:01,990 --> 00:02:03,180
You see,

21
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:06,200
people usually don't want to change

22
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:07,790
when they are comfortable.

23
00:02:07,990 --> 00:02:09,250
They usually only do it

24
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,370
when they hit a wall

25
00:02:10,370 --> 00:02:11,430
and have no choice.

26
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:13,120
But someone like Shengli,

27
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,310
he's always prepared for a rainy day.

28
00:02:14,310 --> 00:02:15,840
His business is doing well,

29
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,360
yet he chose to adapt.

30
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,829
He is extraordinary.

31
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,350
Yeah,

32
00:02:21,690 --> 00:02:23,210
extraordinarily annoying.

33
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:24,140
Listen to me.

34
00:02:25,810 --> 00:02:28,430
It's all thanks to my wife.

35
00:02:31,770 --> 00:02:33,930
It's all because of my wife.

36
00:02:33,950 --> 00:02:34,460
Come on.

37
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:35,250
Keep talking like this.

38
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:36,150
If you speak any louder,

39
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,010
