40
00:02:44,290 --> 00:02:52,630
[Joyful]

41
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:47,500
- Thank you, everyone.
- Thank you.

42
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,579
Thank you.

43
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:50,890
Thank you! Same to you!

44
00:02:55,530 --> 00:02:56,930
Thanks, you too!

45
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:58,790
Here they come.

46
00:02:59,020 --> 00:02:59,750
We're counting on you, Xiaobao.

47
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,320
Okay.

48
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,330
Happy wedding!

49
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,530
- Thank you.
- We're here.

50
00:03:03,530 --> 00:03:05,900
- Come on.
- Right.

51
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:08,410
Should I call her Ranran today,

52
00:03:08,410 --> 00:03:09,710
