132
00:05:41,010 --> 00:05:41,890
Open the door quickly.

133
00:05:41,890 --> 00:05:43,240
If you don't open the door,

134
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,000
I'll...

135
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,320
