138
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:50,710
Yes.

139
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:52,370
If there's another one, your dad will do it.

140
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:53,060
Hurry up.

141
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,659
Tell Xiaobao to open the door.

142
00:05:54,659 --> 00:05:55,409
