143
00:05:55,409 --> 00:05:56,180
You perform.

144
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,300
- Your son listens to you. Hurry up.
- Your son listens to you.

145
00:05:58,300 --> 00:05:59,430
Listens to me?

146
00:05:59,690 --> 00:06:00,640
Well,

147
00:06:00,930 --> 00:06:02,110
