155
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:19,720
Bow.

156
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:20,940
Brother-in-law!

157
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:23,010
Look, I'm your brother-in-law.

158
00:06:23,010 --> 00:06:24,010
We'll get along well in the future.

159
00:06:24,010 --> 00:06:25,130
Open the door first.

160
00:06:25,130 --> 00:06:26,190
I still have

161
00:06:26,220 --> 00:06:27,360
