00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,330
Go, go, go.

289
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,500
Come, groom, stand here.

290
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:33,630
Bride, stand there.

291
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:35,550
Does this car look nice?

292
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:36,980
Hold hands. Hold hands.

293
00:10:36,980 --> 00:10:38,580
Bride and groom, hold hands.

294
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:44,150
[Suyuan Chun Fresh Corn Juice]

295
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:31,130
[Cao Ye Qigong Research Center]

296
00:11:33,370 --> 00:11:35,720
[Paris, France]

297
00:11:51,010 --> 00:11:51,940
Tao Liangliang.

298
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,870
I got hired by the travel agency.

299
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,140
I can start work tomorrow.

300
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,080
In a couple of days,

301
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,100
there will be a small Chinese tour group

302
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:03,050
for me to host.

303
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,940
We'll have an income soon.

304
00:12:04,980 --> 00:12:07,190
I told you you'd be fine.

305
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:09,300
Shall we go to the supermarket?

306
00:12:09,950 --> 00:12:11,950
You have to introduce to me first

307
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:12,800
what tourist attractions

308
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,060
there are around here.

309
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,030
This one

310
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:17,290
is Chaillot Palace.

311
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,990
My hourly rate is very expensive.

312
00:12:21,990 --> 00:12:22,920
Very expensive?

313
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,580
Then tell me,

314
00:12:24,740 --> 00:12:26,360
how can I afford

315
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,050
such an expensive hourly rate?

316
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:29,560
Make me a nice meal.

317
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,370
Sure.

318
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,160
How nice?

319
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:34,210
I want to eat Zhajiangmian.

320
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:35,610
Let's go to the supermarket.

321
00:12:35,610 --> 00:12:36,230
Let's go.

322
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,790
Dear friends,

323
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:42,000
right in front of you

324
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:45,550
is the most famous landmark in Paris, France,

325
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,410
the Eiffel Tower.

326
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:50,670
It was completed in 1889.

327
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:52,050
Ahead,

328
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:54,990
the left side is the Museum of Mankind.

329
00:12:55,050 --> 00:12:56,070
On the right,

330
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:58,860
is the City of Architecture and Heritage.

331
00:13:28,230 --> 00:13:30,980
[Beijing, China]

332
00:13:28,370 --> 00:13:29,720
Come take a look!

333
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:32,260
All down jackets on clearance sale!

334
00:13:32,430 --> 00:13:33,530
Very cheap!

335
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:35,960
Brother, look at this jacket.

336
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,940
Buy one for your girlfriend.

337
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:37,290
Isn't it nice?

338
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:38,220
Just bought one.

339
00:13:38,220 --> 00:13:39,750
Thank you. Just bought one.

340
00:13:40,700 --> 00:13:41,520
Come again.

341
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,730
Meng.

342
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:43,790
Mr. Xu.

343
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:45,290
Why are you doing a clearance sale?

344
00:13:45,290 --> 00:13:47,090
Aren't your goods selling well?

345
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,580
You know how I am.

346
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:52,320
I don't have my own production line.

347
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,240
I rely on

348
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,500
buying and reselling every day.

349
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:56,740
One moment the supplier raises the price,

350
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:58,400
the next, the orders are gone.

351
00:13:58,550 --> 00:14:00,520
Who can stand this?

352
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,210
I borrowed money

353
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:03,670
to stock up on goods these two months.

354
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:05,200
Then some bastard showed up

355
00:14:05,370 --> 00:14:07,120
and used a really dirty trick.

356
00:14:07,370 --> 00:14:09,080
He pushed the price of the same goods

357
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,680
down to the absolute lowest.

358
00:14:10,890 --> 00:14:11,670
With the little money I have,

359
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:12,940
robbing Peter to pay Paul

360
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,200
and tossing it around,

361
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:15,440
the little profit left in the end

362
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,770
isn't even enough to cover the interest.

363
00:14:16,770 --> 00:14:18,250
The market is bad right now.

364
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:19,650
It's not easy for anyone.

365
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,350
If you need any help,

366
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,370
just let me know.

367
00:14:22,910 --> 00:14:23,480
Right.

368
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:26,360
I heard you two negotiated with a factory.

369
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:27,250
Are you planning

370
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:29,110
to start production yourselves?

371
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:31,050
Didn't you just say so yourself?

372
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,890
Relying purely on reselling

373
00:14:32,890 --> 00:14:33,940
is not reliable.

374
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:35,650
- There are too many unstable factors.
- Yes.

375
00:14:35,650 --> 00:14:36,620
So we figured,

376
00:14:36,650 --> 00:14:37,750
instead of tying our money up in goods,

377
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,940
it's better to find a new way out.

378
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,600
We plan

379
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:44,480
to create our own brand.

380
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:46,470
That's great!

381
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:50,130
Zhuang Zhuang's designs are really pretty.

382
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:51,360
If you ask me,

383
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,290
you guys should have

384
00:14:52,290 --> 00:14:53,480
started your own brand

385
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,670
a long time ago.

386
00:14:54,890 --> 00:14:57,320
Okay, thanks for the good word.

387
00:14:58,340 --> 00:14:58,770
Brother,

388
00:14:58,770 --> 00:15:00,360
I have another question for you.

389
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:00,910
Go ahead.

390
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:03,650
A couple of days ago,

391
00:15:03,650 --> 00:15:05,250
I was walking past your door,

392
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,240
and I saw a hiring sign

393
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,160
on your door.

394
00:15:07,530 --> 00:15:09,730
What kind of person are you looking for?

395
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:11,120
The thing is,

396
00:15:11,530 --> 00:15:12,220
you and Zhuang Zhuang

397
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,270
are such nice people.

398
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:14,670
I want to work with you guys.

399
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:15,600
Perfect timing.

400
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,800
We just got our registered brand,

401
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,200
and we're short on hands.

402
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,000
And here you are.

403
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,080
What a coincidence.

404
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:21,870
Hurry up and pack your things.

405
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:23,500
Once you're done, go to my shop.

406
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:23,820
Okay.

407
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:25,250
The first batch of goods for our brand

408
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:25,910
is arriving soon.

409
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,170
I have to go receive it.

410
00:15:28,770 --> 00:15:29,300
Brother.

411
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,120
I heard

412
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,930
