413
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:34,910
It's been jammed since morning.

414
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:35,830
That can't be.

415
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,600
I was second in line to get in today.

416
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,480
Ms. Zhang in front of me

417
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,740
