418
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:41,740
I heard they're not moving goods in.

419
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,290
They were shipping out last night

420
00:15:43,290 --> 00:15:45,020
and haven't finished loading.

421
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,540
Guangfa Commerce.

422
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:49,980
Yeah.

423
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,510
When Chen Guangfa

424
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,570
ships out, it's a huge batch.

425
00:15:54,740 --> 00:15:56,650
The shipment to Russia this month,

426
00:15:56,650 --> 00:15:58,620
It's all being restocked via charter flights.

427
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:00,340
There are six or seven tons of clothes.

428
00:16:00,340 --> 00:16:01,630
No matter how much cargo he has,

429
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:02,340
