430
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,000
other merchants' access.

431
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:05,590
I know, right?

432
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,870
But there's nothing we can do.

433
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:08,980
He is

434
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:10,960
the Down Jacket King of Yabao Road.

435
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,530
You know his relationship

436
00:16:12,530 --> 00:16:14,170
with Manager Wang, don't you?

437
00:16:14,170 --> 00:16:15,250
Should I go take a look with you?

438
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:15,710
No need.

439
00:16:16,510 --> 00:16:17,170
You go ahead.

440
00:16:17,170 --> 00:16:18,170
Hurry up and pack.

441
00:16:18,220 --> 00:16:19,020
I'll go check.

442
00:16:20,270 --> 00:16:22,400
Call me if you need anything, brother.

443
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:28,120
Come take a look.

444
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:30,660
Down jackets on clearance, very cheap.

445
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:41,390
Mr. Chen.

446
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:43,460
Nice to meet you.

447
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,940
Let me introduce myself.

448
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:45,950
I am Xu Shengli,

449
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:48,140
and I also have a shop here.

450
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:56,720
Xu.

451
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,609
Mr. Xu, right?

452
00:17:10,220 --> 00:17:11,220
I've heard of you.

453
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:13,980
In the Russian commercial district,

454
00:17:14,609 --> 00:17:15,810
you are quite famous.

455
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:17,440
You flatter me.

456
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,180
You are the real veteran here.

457
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:20,530
When our shop first opened,

458
00:17:20,530 --> 00:17:21,589
I came to visit you.

459
00:17:21,849 --> 00:17:22,640
You weren't here at the time,

460
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,510
so I just said hello

461
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:24,369
to the manager.

462
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,700
So I thought

463
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,440
I should come visit again.

464
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:30,150
Have some tea.

465
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:33,980
[Guangfa Commerce]

466
00:17:51,250 --> 00:17:52,450
You didn't come today

467
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:54,400
