468
00:17:54,440 --> 00:18:03,610
[Guangfa Commerce]

469
00:17:56,570 --> 00:17:58,570
Then I'll get straight to the point.

470
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:00,360
I just went to the basement.

471
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:01,800
Our unloading area

472
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:02,290
is full of

473
00:18:02,290 --> 00:18:03,900
