474
00:18:03,900 --> 00:18:05,430
My goods are arriving soon,

475
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,510
and it's a large amount.

476
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:07,500
If they pile up at the door,

477
00:18:07,500 --> 00:18:08,520
my goods can't get in

478
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:09,850
and yours can't get out.

479
00:18:10,010 --> 00:18:11,720
Wouldn't that delay your business too?

480
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:12,270
Then we'll have

481
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:14,070
