482
00:18:15,530 --> 00:18:16,200
Your business

483
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,460
has been doing well these past few years.

484
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:19,880
I really appreciate it.

485
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:22,280
The way young people do business nowadays.

486
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:23,510
Especially you.

487
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,640
You look like a scholar,

488
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:28,420
but actually, you have a lot of personality.

489
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:30,190
You're cut out for business.

490
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:33,910
There's something

491
00:18:34,610 --> 00:18:35,870
I want to ask you about.

492
00:18:37,110 --> 00:18:37,570
Why

493
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:39,390
would you switch to down jackets

494
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:43,690
when your leather shoe business is doing so well?

495
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,250
It's a long story.

496
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:51,410
If you're really interested,

497
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,550
we can talk about it in detail some other day.

498
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:55,280
I'm a straightforward person,

499
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,910
so please excuse me, Mr. Chen.

500
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:58,000
Shouldn't we

501
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:00,180
solve the problem at hand right now?

502
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:01,580
What do you say?

503
00:19:12,190 --> 00:19:18,380
[Guangfa Commerce]

504
00:19:17,180 --> 00:19:18,310
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

505
00:19:24,420 --> 00:19:26,280
What time will your goods arrive?

506
00:19:26,650 --> 00:19:28,650
We'll unload by 10:30 at the latest.

507
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:36,820
Before 10:00,

508
00:19:36,940 --> 00:19:38,400
clear the unloading area.

509
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:41,400
Thanks for the favor, Mr. Chen.

510
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:41,850
You're welcome.

511
00:19:41,850 --> 00:19:42,310
Thanks.

512
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:43,750
Just making a friend.

513
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,140
We definitely should.

514
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:47,160
I'll get back to work then.

515
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:49,510
Xu.

516
00:19:49,690 --> 00:19:51,220
[Guangfa Commerce]

517
00:19:53,850 --> 00:19:54,580
Every place

518
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,010
has its own rules.

519
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,030
Every industry

520
00:19:58,030 --> 00:19:59,150
has its own tricks.

521
00:19:59,850 --> 00:20:00,680
Just because

522
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:02,200
the down jacket business has been booming recently,

523
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,050
doesn't mean you should force your way in.

524
00:20:04,050 --> 00:20:06,740
It's really hard to make it work.

525
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:09,700
If I had your leather shoe business,

526
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:11,690
which is so stable.

527
00:20:13,530 --> 00:20:14,590
I wouldn't do anything

528
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:16,650
