532
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:22,920
When we were

533
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:23,980
in the leather shoe business,

534
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,700
we also struggled all the way.

535
00:20:26,290 --> 00:20:27,690
Whether it's easy or not,

536
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,720
you have to do it to know.

537
00:20:30,140 --> 00:20:31,400
Mr. Chen, don't worry.

538
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:34,260
I'm ready to pay my dues.

539
00:20:34,980 --> 00:20:36,780
You are considered

540
00:20:37,610 --> 00:20:38,670
a big brother here.

541
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:40,810
So please look after me from now on.

542
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,090
I'll get to work.

543
00:20:50,580 --> 00:20:59,810
[Beijing MRX Trading Co., Ltd.]

544
00:20:53,010 --> 00:20:53,580
Honey,

545
00:20:53,810 --> 00:20:54,350
