546
00:20:54,350 --> 00:20:55,010
Let me do it.

547
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,100
Let me do it.

548
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,480
Okay, I'm done wiping.

549
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:07,170
MRX.

550
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:09,190
It sounds warm,

551
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:10,550
and has brand warmth.

552
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:12,900
And our logo

553
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:14,630
is designed so well.

554
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:16,000
We actually

555
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,640
have our own brand.

556
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:20,660
This is the first step

557
00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:21,930
of our dream.

558
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:23,380
Then next,

559
00:21:23,610 --> 00:21:25,480
our MRX will...

560
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:26,890
Selling to Russia,

561
00:21:27,010 --> 00:21:27,960
to Eastern Europe,

562
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,300
and to North America.

563
00:21:29,590 --> 00:21:30,670
By then,

564
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:31,900
we won't just

565
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:32,960
have down jackets.

566
00:21:33,070 --> 00:21:34,280
What we'll do is

567
00:21:34,420 --> 00:21:36,890
the MRX brand series.

568
00:21:37,050 --> 00:21:39,500
Menswear, womenswear, kidswear,

569
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:41,720
and custom dresses.

570
00:21:42,010 --> 00:21:43,570
Dresses are called MRX too?

571
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:44,800
Absolutely.

572
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,380
My wife came up with it.

573
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:47,330
It's such a nice name,

574
00:21:47,330 --> 00:21:48,660
we have to keep using it.

575
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,050
Let's

576
00:21:52,050 --> 00:21:53,000
first establish a foothold

577
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,120
here on Yabao Road.

578
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:55,530
Look at how many people

579
00:21:55,530 --> 00:21:57,790
are selling down jackets in this market.

580
00:21:58,090 --> 00:21:59,580
The market is good,

581
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:00,720
