596
00:22:26,570 --> 00:22:28,220
He said the same thing as me?

597
00:22:28,660 --> 00:22:29,650
Pretty much.

598
00:22:30,250 --> 00:22:31,330
Actually, I always feel

599
00:22:31,330 --> 00:22:31,900
that he seems

600
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:34,400
a bit hostile towards us.

601
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:35,900
Him?

602
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:36,550
Come on.

603
00:22:37,070 --> 00:22:37,670
It's here.

604
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:39,660
Hello. Who is Mr. Xu?

605
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:40,270
Hello, I am.

606
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:40,790
Hello.

607
00:22:40,830 --> 00:22:41,700
Um, your goods have arrived.

608
00:22:41,700 --> 00:22:42,330
Come on.

609
00:22:42,530 --> 00:22:43,200
Put it inside.

610
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:44,090
Okay, okay.

611
00:22:44,090 --> 00:22:45,480
Hurry and unload it. Come on.

612
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,910
Come on, put it inside.

613
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,990
Ten boxes. Okay.

614
00:22:50,290 --> 00:22:50,790
Okay.

615
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:52,030
It's okay. We'll do it ourselves.

616
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:52,530
Okay.

617
00:22:54,010 --> 00:22:54,860
Thanks for your hard work.

618
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:56,000
- Here you are.
- It’s OK.

619
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,440
Okay.

620
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:56,880
Thank you.

621
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:57,530
- Thank you.
- If everything is here...

622
00:22:57,530 --> 00:22:58,990
- Yes, yes, yes.
- We’ll leave if there’s nothing else.

623
00:22:58,990 --> 00:22:59,690
Okay.

624
00:23:00,050 --> 00:23:00,550
I'll let you get on.

625
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:01,110
Okay.

626
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:02,420
Let's go. Come on.

627
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:09,210
I'll do it.

628
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,260
So good.

629
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,030
These bulk goods

630
00:23:19,030 --> 00:23:21,160
are made even better than the samples.

631
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:23,550
I'll put them on the models right away.

632
00:23:24,740 --> 00:23:26,570
Now I know why Mr. Chen

633
00:23:26,570 --> 00:23:28,090
is so hostile towards us.

634
00:23:29,050 --> 00:23:30,780
With our quality being so good,

635
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:31,700
he's worried that

636
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:33,860
we'll steal his crown.

637
00:23:33,980 --> 00:23:35,080
Look at you.

638
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,480
No wonder he singled you out.

639
00:23:37,610 --> 00:23:38,960
Let him.

640
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,640
I just tell the truth.

641
00:23:45,980 --> 00:23:46,910
Secretary Sang,

642
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:48,940
is this Chairman Luo

643
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:49,880
the same one

644
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:51,280
Mr. Lu mentioned before,

645
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:53,380
the legend in the investment world?

646
00:23:53,380 --> 00:23:53,790
Yes.

647
00:23:54,570 --> 00:23:55,570
It's not convenient for the chairman

648
00:23:55,570 --> 00:23:57,030
to show up in public often.

649
00:23:57,330 --> 00:23:58,250
Calling you to his home

650
00:23:58,250 --> 00:23:59,510
to help him recuperate

651
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:00,940
shows his trust in you.

652
00:24:01,330 --> 00:24:01,950
When you're out,

653
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:03,480
