654
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:04,010
Okay.

655
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:06,340
By the way,

656
00:24:06,660 --> 00:24:08,360
I must reiterate,

657
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:10,320
You must not tell anyone

658
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:12,080
about today's visit.

659
00:24:12,570 --> 00:24:13,740
You can't breathe a word

660
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:15,460
about what you see and hear either.

661
00:24:15,460 --> 00:24:16,390
Behave yourself

662
00:24:16,530 --> 00:24:17,940
when you see the Chairman.

663
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:19,550
If the Chairman doesn't offer a handshake,

664
00:24:19,550 --> 00:24:21,480
you shouldn't reach out your hand.

665
00:24:36,110 --> 00:24:36,880
Chairman.

666
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:39,920
Impure qi is rising.

667
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:41,420
It's better to spit it out.

668
00:24:46,770 --> 00:24:48,570
I've been coughing a lot lately.

669
00:24:49,290 --> 00:24:50,620
I took a lot of medicine,

670
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:52,810
and hired many doctors,

671
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:57,380
but there's still no improvement.

672
00:24:57,720 --> 00:25:00,180
Because this cough is not an ordinary cough.

673
00:25:01,740 --> 00:25:03,030
What's the difference?

674
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:04,230
In 1994,

675
00:25:04,250 --> 00:25:05,980
a Japanese research institute

676
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:06,810
started

677
00:25:06,810 --> 00:25:08,340
a study on water molecules.

678
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,680
Water molecules?

679
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:13,150
I'll make it short.

680
00:25:13,270 --> 00:25:14,220
It means

681
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:15,700
pouring the same water

682
00:25:15,850 --> 00:25:17,450
into different containers.

683
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,030
One container is labeled

684
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:20,380
with beautiful blessings,

685
00:25:20,380 --> 00:25:21,380
and the other side

686
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:23,240
is labeled with vicious curses.

687
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:25,070
Both put into the freezer at the same time.

688
00:25:25,070 --> 00:25:26,720
After the water becomes ice crystals,

689
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,240
observing them under a microscope,

690
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:30,940
they found their forms are completely different.

691
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:31,640
So,

692
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:34,030
because of an encounter in my childhood,

693
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:35,400
I can inject my thoughts

694
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,700
into your body

695
00:25:36,900 --> 00:25:38,440
to communicate

696
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,400
with the water molecules in your body,

697
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,860
making them stronger.

698
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:43,400
You will naturally get well and recover.

699
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,690
Sounds quite interesting.

700
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:58,240
Did you have fun, my baby?

701
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:02,180
I don't want to go home.

702
00:26:04,330 --> 00:26:06,100
Seems like you're tired from playing.

703
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:07,160
I have a guest here.

704
00:26:07,770 --> 00:26:08,770
You go rest first.

705
00:26:15,890 --> 00:26:17,770
Let's continue.

706
00:26:18,180 --> 00:26:18,550
Okay.

707
00:26:24,980 --> 00:26:26,700
Thank you for your hard work, Master Cao.

708
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:27,890
It's my duty.

709
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,720
The chairman's illness

710
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,150
is caused by overwork

711
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,400
and the accumulation of stagnant qi in his body.

712
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,320
It's not mild,

713
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:35,350
but don't worry.

714
00:26:35,570 --> 00:26:37,670
As long as I use my mind

715
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:39,200
to transform the water molecules in his body

716
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,190
a few more times,

717
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,770
he will surely recover.

718
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:44,990
Thank you, Master Cao.

719
00:26:45,090 --> 00:26:46,090
Thank you so much.

720
00:26:46,610 --> 00:26:47,690
You're welcome.

721
00:26:47,850 --> 00:26:49,350
It's because of your trust.

722
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:50,660
The chairman also gave me an opportunity.

723
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:52,120
I must thank you very much.

724
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:53,980
Master Cao.

725
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:56,330
I suppose you have heard Mr. Lu mention this before.

726
00:26:56,330 --> 00:26:57,280
Our chairman

727
00:26:57,380 --> 00:26:58,880
