728
00:26:58,880 --> 00:27:01,550
All the projects he invests in are highly profitable.

729
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,450
I hope

730
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,350
I will have the chance in the future

731
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:04,670
