737
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:16,400
They were all collected by Miss Luo.

738
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,210
So this Miss Luo

739
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,590
truly has extraordinary taste.

740
00:27:27,110 --> 00:27:28,050
Perhaps because of this

741
00:27:28,050 --> 00:27:29,310
extraordinary taste,

742
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:30,920
she hasn't met

743
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:31,940
her Mr. Right yet.

744
00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:37,950
Master Cao, you are also a young talent.

745
00:27:38,770 --> 00:27:40,180
Are you married?

746
00:27:46,590 --> 00:27:48,110
Don't worry, honey.

747
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:50,090
I've checked the quality of our goods.

748
00:27:50,090 --> 00:27:51,220
Everything is fine.

749
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:52,050
Okay.

750
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:54,150
Shengli, Zhuangzhuang.

751
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:56,090
The garage has been registered.

752
00:27:56,090 --> 00:27:57,180
When customers come to pick up the goods,

753
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,590
