754
00:27:58,590 --> 00:27:59,310
Thank you.

755
00:27:59,330 --> 00:28:00,590
You really know your stuff.

756
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:01,250
Not at all.

757
00:28:04,090 --> 00:28:04,740
Mr. Xu.

758
00:28:05,030 --> 00:28:06,120
Mr. Anton.

759
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:06,920
Welcome.

760
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:07,900
Welcome.

761
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:10,050
- Have a seat.
- Come on. Have a seat. Get some water.

762
00:28:10,050 --> 00:28:11,350
We have prepared all the goods.

763
00:28:11,350 --> 00:28:12,480
Let's inspect them.

764
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:14,920
No need to inspect.

765
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,210
I have seen them many times.

766
00:28:16,210 --> 00:28:17,450
You did very well.

767
00:28:17,850 --> 00:28:19,850
Thank you for your trust, Mr. Anton.

768
00:28:20,110 --> 00:28:21,790
How long will the relabeling take?

769
00:28:21,790 --> 00:28:23,270
I'll pick them up in a week.

770
00:28:27,420 --> 00:28:27,980
Relabeling?

771
00:28:27,980 --> 00:28:30,790
