774
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:39,520
Mr. Anton, please don't worry.

775
00:28:39,570 --> 00:28:41,170
It's just replacing labels.

776
00:28:41,330 --> 00:28:42,380
We can rework quickly.

777
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:44,110
- It'll be done in a week.
- Meng,

778
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,200
