800
00:29:30,090 --> 00:29:31,360
I'm sorry, Mr. Anton.

801
00:29:31,500 --> 00:29:33,360
Our store doesn't sell OEM goods.

802
00:29:34,010 --> 00:29:35,770
We're not selling these 600 pieces.

803
00:29:35,770 --> 00:29:37,380
The MRXs are made in China.

804
00:29:39,140 --> 00:29:39,860
Mr. Anton,

805
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:42,210
