806
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:43,530
We haven't touched it.

807
00:29:43,660 --> 00:29:44,590
You can check it.

808
00:29:54,140 --> 00:29:54,980
Take care.

809
00:30:05,090 --> 00:30:06,490
Shengli, Zhuangzhuang.

810
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,200
Don't be mad.

811
00:30:09,290 --> 00:30:10,750
Actually, shipping goods to Russia,

812
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:11,880
there really is such an

813
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:12,810
unwritten rule.

814
00:30:13,250 --> 00:30:14,310
There are also many

815
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,640
