818
00:30:18,610 --> 00:30:19,420
Some even use glue

819
00:30:19,420 --> 00:30:20,550
to stick them directly.

820
00:30:20,550 --> 00:30:21,290
Once they pass the inspection,

821
00:30:21,290 --> 00:30:22,850
they can be blown off with a hair dryer.

822
00:30:22,850 --> 00:30:24,640
Then no one will know they're made in China.

823
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,000
People buying clothes don't care about this either.

824
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,860
Our job is making money, isn't it?

825
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,020
We care about that.

826
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:34,960
Have a seat, Meng.

827
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:38,000
Before this,

828
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,610
