855
00:31:32,610 --> 00:31:34,120
Right, and you have me.

856
00:31:34,250 --> 00:31:34,790
Right.

857
00:31:35,140 --> 00:31:36,870
The most important thing today

858
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:37,960
is that Meng

859
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:40,580
